divisions among democrats on the level of 
defense spending widened as the senate budget committee chairman 
questioned why deep cuts can only be achieved by drastic reductions 
in military personnel 
i must disagree with your view that the defense spending level 
in the senate budget resolution cannot be reached without 
unacceptable disruption to americas military establishment 
