defense workers 
this economic conversion theme evolving in legislation and 
campaign pitches like those of heath and delauro involves a range 
of proposals to retool factories redirect research and retrain 
workers while cushioning economic shocks 
the policy holds obious appeal for defensedependent regions of 
new england virginia california texas colorado and new york 
