<TEXT>
americas favorite car of the 1980s isnt resting on its 
laurels for the 1991 model year the ford escort is growing 
adding more hiproom and shoulder room in the rear more glass area 
up front and a new engine 
its also becoming more aerodynamic and improving its fuel 
efficiency 
nearly a decade ago americans came to know and love the 
mildmannered escort the vehicle that ford called its world 
car because it would be sold in many countries 
as the 1980s unfolded the escort subcompact was repeatedly at 
the top of the pack of favorite us nameplates by the end of the 
decade more than 346 million escorts had been sold in this 
country far outdistancing the no 2 nameplate the honda accord 
but ford motor co knew the old escort needed upgrading annual 
sales peaked at around 524500 in 1985 and the no 2 us 
automaker wanted to attract buyers of import cars to the escort 
the car was very good but it was almost a decade old said 
mike sullivan ford division marketing plans manager for the escort 
it was not quite as modern as the honda civic and toyota 
corolla the new escort is virtually all new very modern its not 
second fiddle to any car 
indeed the 1991 ford escort lx 4door hatchback test car was 
admirable in furnishing a back seat that can really be used for 
more than stowing briefcases and shopping bags though three 
goodsized adults might find it confining two adults would be in 
decent shape sullivan noted that ford added 25 inches of hiproom 
and more than 1 inch of shoulder room to the 2door escort 
i had a couple inches of clearance above my head to the roofline 
while sitting on the nicely cushioned cloth back seat and my legs 
were even extended a bit with the front seat back a bit 
with the front seats back all the way i tucked my feet under 
the front seats and my knees still werent crushed into the back of 
the front seatbacks 
in the 4door test car the rear seatback is divided and either 
side can fold down to allow room for long items in the hatchback 
the escort lx rode solidly for a little car i didnt feel 
particularly vulnerable to road bumps the powertrain has its own 
subframe to help reduce vibration and noise and new independent 
front and rear strut suspension kept the ride from being punishing 
i could hear some road noise and the 19liter sequential 
electronic fuelinjected fourcylinder engine teamed with the 
optional fourspeed automatic transmission jerked a bit a few 
times i also noticed when the air conditioner running at full 
blast tapped into the engines power 
still the engine can deliver up to 88 horsepower while 
propelling an escort thats heavier than its predecessor all 
without losing fuel economy a smoother exterior design helps too 
bringing the escorts drag coefficient which indicates the ease 
with which the car moves through the air down from 039 to 035 
of course i wasnt expecting a race car from the escort lx 
overall there was just no getting around the fact that the escort 
lx was simple decent transportation packaged in a body that was 
plainly pleasing inside and out i admired the way the car 
squeezed into awkward parking spots how easy it was to read the 
large analog gauges how comfortable it was to get used to this 
vehicle 
the average price of a 1991 escort is up about 25 percent from 
its comparably equipped predecessor but base prices ranging from 
7565 for a 2door hatchback to 11063 for an escort gt sport 
model remain within reach of many potential buyers 
ford expects escort purchasers to have a median age of 34 with 
median household income of 30000 a year about 45 percent will be 
men and at least a third of buyers will be college graduates 
sullivan said 
he added that many features such as better computerized engine 
control and tinted glass are now part of the standard escort 
vehicle 
comparisons with competitors such as the civic which starts at 
more than 6600 for a 2door hatchback with manual transmission 
and corolla which starts at more than 8700 are therefore 
difficult sullivan said 
consumer reports magazine ranked 1987 and 1988 escorts worse 
than average in owner reports of trouble but ford said the 1991 
escort will usher in a new era at ford in terms of quality 
manufacturing and design 
the company looks to sell 400000 escorts a year 
